Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家為什麼都會聚集到這兒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了熱熱鬧鬧地吃吃東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是在哪兒都能做的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.87,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(250,320)\fad(300,300)}然後、朝著下一個景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺那兒的空氣都不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  我今天也是來享受的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就買了這些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買點東西  就麻煩楓同學做飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的笨拙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,番茄醬燴飯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把蔬菜先煮熟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後加入法式清湯和番茄醬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把飯放進去後攪拌3分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請嘗一下味道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:00:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去買什麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種各樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便選的材料也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是隨便選的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是基本素材都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真不錯  在大太陽下做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你買的原來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  接著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵姐看上去很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她原來更加拘謹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點變化了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們鬧過頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:01:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個功能表是從哪兒學的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從料理書上看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有實質內容的對話持續著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這並不讓人感到乏味無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而讓人覺得十分舒暢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始理解為什麼人們會聚集到這兒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是為了確認對方是否幸福才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空真寬廣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡也看不到銀河啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好歹也算是城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果是在山上的話就能看到喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  小葵你也能去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己覺得做不到的事才會做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多數的情況下只要努力就能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒有仰望過星空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一旦有興趣了  感覺就能開始看清
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又能和其它事物產生聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河嗎  真想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  去看銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
